## Build Script Behavior

`scripts/build-tokens.js` adds `px` suffix to number tokens matching these patterns:
- `spacing/`
- `corner-radius/`
- `stroke/`
- `font/size`
- `max-width/`
- `screens/`

`font/leading` is **not** in this list. Line-height tokens output as unitless values.

## Do / Do Not

- **Do** use `var(--font-leading-*)` for all line-heights
- **Do** use `@include` text-style mixins (they reference the tokens)
- **Do not** add `font/leading` to `needsPxUnits()` in build script
- **Do not** hardcode pixel line-heights in component SCSS
- **Do not** remove `ascent-override`, `descent-override`, `line-gap-override` from `_fonts.scss`
